dc_title_s: Map Showing Riparian lands located North of Emergency Fleet Corp't'n
dc_description_s: Map shows area to be dredged in Newark Bay. Area to be dredged is within the newly implemented U.S. bulkhead/pierhead lines of 1916.|The westernmost point is the shoreline of Newark Bay, continuing north is Avenue R, continuing east & south is the U.S. Govt. Channel within the Newark Bay.
